# quick-smoke-entrypoint

## Summary

Keep `pnpm smoke` as a bounded preflight that prints a short operator summary plus canonical manual-smoke doc links.

## Accepted Scope

- verify the canonical manual-smoke docs exist before printing the summary
- run the focused docs contract test as the bounded preflight
- fail explicitly when any canonical doc is missing

## Out of Scope

- Docker or host automation
- broader CLI workflow changes
- build or packaging changes
